{"tid":2153313,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發現男朋友偷食元氣壽司","createTime":"2020-08-12T12:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T13:37:49.000Z","uid":1734,"like":12,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f22141e81904817d806e3c0933f629a5b3dad6c5","tid":2153313,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"本身我同男朋友因為方便返工所以一齊係個區合租左個單位<br />\n但依加因為我放多左no pay所以有時會返屋企陪下屋企人係屋企人個邊訓<br />\n冇返去兩晚，頭先我上返去夾租個度見倒個垃圾袋入面有個元氣膠袋同壽司盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我text佢問佢附近咁多野食做咩食元氣<br />\n佢竟然發返我脾氣鬧我<br />\n又話返工好趕無時間買其他野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話你估我似你咩成撚日咁得閒周圍hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD男人真係好蠢，寧願你偷食但瞞住我，但比人斷正仲要發老脾講到好似我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39706198ce94ccfc18224788e02743bad05e8e8","tid":2153313,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"你男朋友真係好衰"},{"pid":"4afc680851459475f79c5c6b0da3c6e41e4792c8","tid":2153313,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"應唔應該私了你男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d455fc277e9e75ed86f3152839014d800cbbd22b","tid":2153313,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">屌你老母抄post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d7e5b2adf30d18a839ff36f16bb19792dfad18fc","tid":2153313,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39706198ce94ccfc18224788e02743bad05e8e8","tid":2153313,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re